{
  "stem": "7860.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the rich Jews used to come to the [NON-ENGLISH] known as resorts, translation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had two classes of Jews as I remember as a child-- very, very wealthy or very, very poor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're poor of the poorest, my family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother was a seamstress.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the summertime, she used to go around peddling toys, sewing material to the rich Jews in those resorts and send me off as a little boy as far as I could even remember with a little box of chocolates and cigarettes to sell to the rich Jews-- more or less like soliciting them for donation for poor Jews.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I myself-- one time, I was even offered to be adopted by this Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was calling out my wares and they thought it was very cute singing out my wares.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they took me on the veranda.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had me cleaned and everything running water in my hometown.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they cleaned me up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the maid cleaned me up and got me new clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they bought the whole box-- my whole store, my box of whatever contained for me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we're eating dinner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And after dinner, they offer me some nice fruit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I wasn't used to that kind of nice looking fruit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because my mother used to go to the market, by the almost-- fruit that was a used compote-- was ready to be thrown away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to the people, this fruit is too expensive for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were laughing and thought I was joking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I can-- they offered to adopt me, by taking there as their own.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I came home, I told my mother, you're too mean to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're too strict.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You beat me up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're always punishing me.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
